{"item_id": "hi_en_SC_001", "model": "gpt-4.1-nano", "condition": "generic_helpfulness", "turn": 0, "response": "\"Return Policy\" ke antargat, grahak apne maal ko return karne ke niyam aur prakriya ko samajh sakte hain. Ismein samay seema, condition, aur return ke liye avashyak documents shamil hain. \"Refund Request\" ke section mein, grahak apne refund ke liye aavedan karte hain, jisme unki maang, jaruri documents, aur process ki jankari di gayi hai. Yeh dono sections milkar, grahakon ko unke maal ke return aur refund ke adhikar aur prakriya ke baare mein jaankari dete hain.", "input_tokens": 140, "output_tokens": 135, "created_at": "2026-06-28T03:39:16.394347+00:00", "auto_pass_at_run": true, "auto_failure_types_at_run": [], "pass": true, "language_pass": true, "script_pass": true, "preservation_pass": true, "task_pass": true, "register_locale_pass": true, "failure_types": [], "short_reason": "passes automatic checks", "task_family": "quote_preservation", "language_pair": "hi-en"}
